---
import { Image } from "@astrojs/image/components";

import ButtonLiveProduction from "../../../components/ButtonLiveProduction/ButtonLiveProduction.astro";
import IconYortime from "../Icons/IconYortime.astro";
import ProjectSlider from "../ProjectSlider.astro";
import IconLaravel from "../Icons/IconLaravel.astro";
import IconMysql from "../Icons/IconMysql.astro";
---

<article
  style={{ transform: "perspective(75em) rotateX(18deg)" }}
  id="project-natatoko"
  class="relative z-10 mx-auto max-w-[1244px] overflow-hidden py-20 sm:rounded-3xl"
>
  <!-- Outnament Lines (Top) -->
  <Image
    format="webp"
    src="/images/project-ournament-lines.png"
    width="1000"
    height="1000"
    loading="lazy"
    alt=""
    class="pointer-events-none absolute left-0 top-0 z-0 min-w-[600px] sm:min-w-[1000px]"
  />

  <!-- Outnament Lines (Bottom) -->
  <Image
    format="webp"
    src="/images/project-ournament-lines-btm-red.png"
    loading="lazy"
    width="1000"
    height="1000"
    alt=""
    class="pointer-events-none absolute bottom-0 right-0 z-0 min-w-[500px] sm:min-w-[1000px]"
  />

  <div class="relative z-10 px-5 sm:px-10 lg:px-16">
    <h3 class="sr-only">Natatoko</h3>

    <IconYortime />

    <h4 class="sr-only">Yortime - Your Ultimate Workforce Management Companion</h4>

    <p class="mt-10 text-lg !leading-150 text-dark sm:text-2xl">
      <strong class="font-semibold"
        >Introducing Yortime, your go-to workforce management (WFM) app designed to simplify and optimize your
        workforce-related tasks.
      </strong>
      Whether you're a small startup, a mid-sized company, or a large enterprise, Yortime is here to make managing your workforce
      efficient and hassle-free.
    </p>

     <h4 class="text-2xl font-semibold leading-140 text-dark sm:text-[32px] mt-5">Key Features of Yortime:</h4>
    <ol class="text-lg !leading-150 text-dark sm:text-2xl">
      <li>
        <strong>Seamless Scheduling:</strong>
        <ul>
          <li>- Create, manage, and share forecasting & schedules effortlessly.</li>
          <li>- Intelligent shift allocation based on employee availability and skills.</li>
          <li>- Say goodbye to scheduling conflicts.</li>
        </ul>
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Precise Time and Attendance:</strong>
        <ul>
          <li>- Accurate tracking of employee working hours.</li>
          <li>- Streamlined clock-in and clock-out processes.</li>
          <li>- Generate detailed attendance reports for payroll and compliance.</li>
        </ul>
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Leave and Absence Management:</strong>
        <ul>
          <li>- Simplify leave requests and approvals.</li>
          <li>- Keep track of employee vacations, sick leave, and other absences.</li>
          <li>- Ensure compliance with labor laws and company policies.</li>
        </ul>
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Performance Insights:</strong>
        <ul>
          <li>- Real-time analytics dashboard for workforce performance.</li>
          <li>- Monitor productivity, attendance, and efficiency.</li>
          <li>- Identify trends and areas for improvement.</li>
        </ul>
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Mobile Accessibility:</strong>
        <ul>
          <li>- Access Yortime on-the-go, anytime, and from any device.</li>
          <li>- Employees can view schedules, request time off, and clock in/out using their smartphones.</li>
          <li>- Managers can make real-time adjustments and approvals wherever they are.</li>
        </ul>
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Seamless Integration:</strong>
        <ul>
          <li>- Yortime easily integrates with your existing HR and payroll systems.</li>
          <li>- Import and export data effortlessly, ensuring data consistency and accuracy.</li>
        </ul>
      </li>
    </ol>
  </div>

  <div class="portfolio-images">
    <ProjectSlider
      project="yortime"
      images={Array.from({ length: 13 }, (_, i) => ({
        url: `/images/projects/yortime/@yortime${i + 1}.png`,
        alt: "Yortime",
      }))}
    />
  </div>

  <div class="relative z-10 px-5 sm:px-10 lg:px-16">
    <h4 class="text-2xl font-semibold leading-140 text-dark sm:text-[32px] mt-5">Benefits of Yortime:</h4>
    <ul class="text-lg !leading-150 text-dark sm:text-2xl">
      <li>
        <strong>Enhanced Efficiency:</strong>
        <ul>
          <li>- Automate repetitive tasks, such as scheduling and attendance tracking.</li>
          <li>- Free up valuable time for HR professionals and managers to focus on strategic initiatives.</li>
        </ul>
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Cost Savings:</strong>
        <ul>
          <li>- Reduce labor costs by optimizing shift assignments and minimizing overtime.</li>
          <li>- Minimize errors in payroll calculations and compliance issues.</li>
        </ul>
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Happy Employees:</strong>
        <ul>
          <li>- Empower employees with self-service options for scheduling and leave requests.</li>
          <li>- Promote fair and transparent scheduling practices, improving job satisfaction.</li>
        </ul>
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Informed Decision-Making:</strong>
        <ul>
          <li>- Access real-time analytics and insights to make data-driven workforce decisions.</li>
          <li>- Adjust staffing levels based on historical data and current demand.</li>
        </ul>
      </li>
    </ul>
    <h4 class="text-2xl font-semibold leading-140 text-dark sm:text-[32px] mt-5">Conclusion:</h4>
    <p class="text-lg !leading-150 text-dark sm:text-2xl">
      Yortime is your all-in-one solution for workforce management. Simplify complex processes, improve efficiency, and
      gain valuable insights to stay competitive in today's business environment. Say goodbye to scheduling headaches
      and payroll errorsâ€”experience the future of workforce management with Yortime today!
    </p>

